story: The Commissars are a group of Communists who were the first, and last, test subjects of Project Pavlov. Project Pavlov was a Soviet plan to use the captured body of the deceased Claw to give mental control powers to ordinary humans. The project was a success even beyond this goal, which each of the four test subjects gaining a different power from the Claw: mind control, super strength, energy blasts, and growth.
The members of the Commissars are Collective, the New Man, the New Woman, and the People's Hero.
